   <p><strong>Configuration</strong></p>
<p>This screen will allow you to define the Basic Configuration for the site</p>

<p>Enter the Maximum Data Storage Period (In Days). Enter 0 for no limit. The data beyond this period will be deleted by the House Keeping Service</p>

<p>The Last Generated Sensor Number is displayed in a disabled field</p>

<p>Click on the 'Reset Sensor Number' button to reset the Sensor Counter to 0. <font color="red"></font></p>

<p>Click on the 'Save Configuration' button to save the configuration settings</p>


</body>
